{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/Java/start_gradle_project/gradle_start_project/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"fe59af65-455b-57c1-bfd9-531d75bcf7c4","html":"<h2 id=\"환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>환경</h2>\n<hr>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">종류</th>\n<th>환경</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OS</td>\n<td>M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IDE</td>\n<td>Intellij(2022.1.2)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"gralde-프로젝트-시작하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gralde-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gralde 프로젝트 시작하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"gradle-install-hombrew\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-install-hombrew\" aria-label=\"gradle install hombrew permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Install Hombrew</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://gradle.org/install/\">Gradle Installation Documents</a></p>\n<p>Gradle 공식 문서에 따라 설치하도록 합니다. Hombrew 로 설치하는 것 역시 권장 방법이므로 터미널에 다음과 같이 입력 후 실행합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gradle</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"1-프로젝트-시작-폴더-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성</h3>\n<p>Gradle 프로젝트를 생성하기 전에 해당 프로젝트를 시작할 폴더를 새로 만듭니다. 폴더 명과 별개로 프로젝트 이름은 따로 지정할 수도 있습니다. 방법은 아래 말씀드리겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"> <span class=\"token comment\"># ex) mkdir 프로젝트_폴더_이름</span>\n\n <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> demo-java\n\n <span class=\"token comment\"># 생성한 프로젝트로 이동</span>\n <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> demo-java</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-gradle-프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-gradle-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 gradle 프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성</h3>\n<p>폴더로 이동한 후에 아래 명령어를 입력합니다. 입력 후에는 몇 가지 옵션을 선택하여 프로젝트를 새로 생성합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gradle init</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.555555555555554%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"stat_gradle_new_project\"\n        title=\"stat_gradle_new_project\"\n        src=\"/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/1f083/gradle_start_project-init-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-1.png 180w,\n/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-1.png 360w,\n/static/863201865cf52b583e00a95b8a8b04d2/1f083/gradle_start_project-init-1.png 660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>생성하고자 하는 프로젝트의 타입을 선택합니다. 저는 이번에 2, “application”을 선택하여 진행하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 658px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.22222222222222%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAWklEQVQY062POwoAIRQDX+dfRFBREbz/JWdx622ELYakSUIk58wYg1or3nustWitSSm9KiJ3KKVYa1FKuQ9/4Zxj701r7Z/Cc3nOSe8dYwwxRkIIrz9jR2+uPzHhVDcACwltAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"language_select\"\n        title=\"language_select\"\n        src=\"/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/889a4/gradle_start_project-init-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-2.png 180w,\n/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-2.png 360w,\n/static/7e0273a4499c67e4cc15c258b02d3842/889a4/gradle_start_project-init-2.png 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 프로젝트의 언어를 선택합니다. 저는 “java”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 656px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAATElEQVQI15XMuw3AIAwAUZuCj0EyEg2Ihv2XPJRMkBTXXPFkjME5h703MUZKKaSUEJHfqSrygGst5pyYGe5OrZXWGr13cs7vDyF8Ai+HAirTcZEUSwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bulid script dsl\"\n        title=\"bulid script dsl\"\n        src=\"/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/748f4/gradle_start_project-init-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-3.png 180w,\n/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-3.png 360w,\n/static/36e5e2f36afb9f0407863f230dec2808/748f4/gradle_start_project-init-3.png 656w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 script DSL을 선택합니다. 저는 “groovy”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 661px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAbklEQVQY052QOwoAIRQDVUREQbEQxC9+7n/FLD7YemGLaVJMQlgIAbVWtNZgrYVzDlJKMMb+oZTCGIOknPP/opeUEq3rvRM5Z1r54r2HMQZaa9zyT+GckyR7bxKec1BKwc3XWogx4pbeG4QQn8IHee9X087By/YAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"select_test_framwork\"\n        title=\"select_test_framwork\"\n        src=\"/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/0012b/gradle_start_project-init-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-4.png 180w,\n/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-4.png 360w,\n/static/31ba56aad2af9be476b32902cca80a5d/0012b/gradle_start_project-init-4.png 661w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 661px) 100vw, 661px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 테스트 프레임워크를 선택합니다. 선택할 수 있는 테스트 프레임워크는 여러개가 존재하지만 저는 “junit jufiter”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 577px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.777777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAhUlEQVQI111OwQrFIAzT60BkTufcEFF0HsT//7w8Wthg7xCSpm1a4ZzDdV04zxMhBFBN2nvPNel933mGesdxQCkFIQSklJBSsH5hjOHl3jtSSrjvG7VWRinlZQpfloVDPgH/yDnzQmuNec6JGCN/Yq1l7zk0xmD/+Zbm6JDWGuu6Yts2/ADBX0qj8yyrxgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"insert_project_name\"\n        title=\"insert_project_name\"\n        src=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/gradle_start_project-init-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 180w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 360w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 577w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 프로젝트 명을 입력합니다. 디폴트 값은 폴더의 이름을 따라가지만 다른 프로젝트 명을 입력할 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p>설정을 전부 끝마쳤다면 설정한 옵션에 맞춰 Gradle 프로젝트가 생성됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\">환경</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gralde-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#gradle-install-hombrew\">Gradle Install Hombrew</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-gradle-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"환경 종류 환경 OS M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4) IDE Intellij(2022.1.2) Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기 Gradle Install Hombrew Gradle Installation Documents Gradle 공식 문서에 따라 설치하도록 합니다. Hombrew 로 설치하는 것 역시 권장 방법이므로 터미널에 다음과 같이 입력 후 실행합니다. 1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성 Gradle 프로젝트를 생성하기 전에 해당 프로젝트를 시작할 폴더를 새로 만듭니다. 폴더 명과 별개로 프로젝트 이름은 따로 지정할 수도 있습니다. 방법은 아래 말씀드리겠습니다. 2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성 폴더로 이동한 후에 아래 명령어를 입력합니다. 입력 후에는 몇 가지 옵션을 선택하여 프로젝트를 새로 생성합니다.  생성하고자 하는 프로젝트의 타입을 선택합니다. 저는 이번에 2, “application”을 선택하여 진행하겠습니다.  다음은 프로젝트의 언어를 선택합니다. 저는 “ja…","frontmatter":{"date":"January 28, 2022","title":"[Gradle] Gradle project 시작하기","categories":"Java","author":"chanjin_ahn","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/Java/start_gradle_project/gradle_start_project/"}},"next":{"id":"e93e9f50-9432-5506-a6db-bdb4a316aeae","html":"<p>이번 포스팅에서는 기존 WAS를 Tomcat에서 undertow로 변경해보겠습니다. tomcat은 오래전부터 사용된 WAS이나 아쉬운 점이 많아 사용 빈도가 줄고 있다고 합니다. 그래서 undertow로 바꿔보도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"라이브러리-가져오기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EA%B0%80%EC%A0%B8%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"라이브러리 가져오기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>라이브러리 가져오기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"기존-tomcat-라이브러리-제외하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-tomcat-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"기존 tomcat 라이브러리 제외하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존 Tomcat 라이브러리 제외하기</h3>\n<p>tomcat은 사용하지 않을 예정이므로 제외합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    configurations <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        all<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            // was tomcat 제외\n            <span class=\"token key atrule\">exclude module</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'spring-boot-starter-tomcat'</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"undertow-라이브러리-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#undertow-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"undertow 라이브러리 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>undertow 라이브러리 추가</h3>\n<p>버전은 본인의 상황에 맞게 maven repository 에서 가져오시면 됩니다.\nundertow 라이브러리와 autobulid 를 위한 devtools 를 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    dependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">implementation group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'org.springframework.boot'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'spring-boot-starter-undertow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2.6.3'</span>\n        developmentOnly 'org.springframework.boot<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>spring<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>boot<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>devtools'\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"applicationyml-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#applicationyml-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"applicationyml 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>application.yml 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"undertow--autobuliddevtools-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#undertow--autobuliddevtools-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"undertow  autobuliddevtools 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>undertow + autobulid(devtools) 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    <span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">spring</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">config</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">activate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">on-profile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"common\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">devtools</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">livereload</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">restart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">server</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">port</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>설정에 대한 프로파일 명을 <strong>common</strong> 로 지정합니다. 해당 프로파일을 불러올 경우의 설정을 정의할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>spring.devtools.livereload.enabled=true: view 파일의 수정 사항을 즉각 반영합니다.</li>\n<li>spring.devtools.restart.enabled=true: java 파일의 수정 사항을 즉각 반영합니다.</li>\n<li>server.port=8080: 프로젝트의 포트를 지정합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"결과-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"결과 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결과 확인</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"기존-tomcat-환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-tomcat-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"기존 tomcat 환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.2